                            <comment id="227911" author="adilger" created="Tue, 15 May 2018 20:51:27 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;It would probably be OK, but it is also tricky since components can be added to existing files, while it is not possible to do this with plain layouts.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
